              <div class="ms-lg-4 font-size-13"><span class="rounded ms-1  ps-1 pe-1 bg-info">Developpement web </span><span class="rounded ms-1  ps-1 pe-1  bg-light">Antananarivo</span><span class=" ms-1 ps-1 pe-1 rounded bg-danger">Remote</span></div>
            
